works.description: For sommeliers, the importance of a bottle of wine is judged with multiple criterions such as age, grape of the wine, body of the wine and its intricate flavorings. For many, wines are a collector’s item, as shown in our coverage of the Most Expensive Wines and also the Botega-Denise Fecil limited edition collector’s wine. A new wine collection in form of the Methusulah’s Armour de Deutz range of Champagne shall be a source of pride for its owners and other wine tasters alike.
